567
00:59:32,080 --> 00:59:36,240
if this doesn't happen. You end up with 
something that looks like a television remote,  

568
00:59:36,240 --> 00:59:41,480
where there's a Netflix button over here... It's 
like you can reverse [inaudible 00:59:41] from  

569
00:59:41,480 --> 00:59:50,760
the remote control. That's important.
Using these moments and also bringing  

570
00:59:50,760 --> 00:59:56,040
decision making inwards to go and 
say, hey, let's have very efficient  

