01:01:23,560 --> 01:01:25,360
it's absolutely full of interns. It's great.

590
01:01:25,360 --> 01:01:30,480
Oh, man. Love interns, so much energy. This 
idea that you shared about building one product,  

591
01:01:30,480 --> 01:01:33,600
building towards one vision, this actually 
reminds me of something that came up basically  

592
01:01:33,600 --> 01:01:37,680
every time I had someone from Shopify 
