01:01:43,040 --> 01:01:46,240
where the founder has this 100-year 
vision of where the product needs to go  

595
01:01:46,240 --> 01:01:48,840
and working backwards from that.
Can you just speak to that,  

596
01:01:48,840 --> 01:01:52,120
of that way of operating, why you find 
that helpful, how that actually works?

597
01:01:52,120 --> 01:02:02,440
I talk about look in the future and then think 
backwards a lot. What would we want to have done  

598
01:02:02,440 --> 01:02:08,720
20 years ago on this, or 10 or 5 years ago? 
What's the decision our future selves would  

